### Summary

Issue #294 (Phase 4 power-user navigation) has three sub-issues: command palette (#282), keyboard shortcuts (#283), and calendar view (#284). All sub-implementations exist in the codebase, but one gap remains: **the command palette has no "Switch to Calendar View" command**, even though #284 requires calendar to be accessible "from sidebar view toggle or command palette." The sidebar calendar toggle is additionally gated behind `showGraphView` (100+ Things), making calendar completely unreachable for users with 50–99 Things.

